grammar denoted by the type $FGRAMMAR$.
=SML
datatype ''a €FSYM› = €FTerm› of ''a
	| €FNonTerm› of FNONTERM;
type ''a €FPRODUCTION› = NONTERMINAL * (''a FSYM array array);
type ''a €FGRAMMAR› = ''a FPRODUCTION array;
